User: peachey  Tue Sep 14 07:39:54 PDT 2004
st_graph/src

Modified Files:
	RootEngine.cxx 
Log Message:
Connect Root widget slots/signals explicitly to their parent RootFrames.
Use a default receiver to allow main frames by default to terminate the
event loop when they are closed. Do not add RootFrame's ancestor frame
to the list of frames; instead call its display/unDisplay directly.
Tweak the handling of RootPlotHist to work with this change. Return to
using STGMainFrame for main frames, because without overriding
TGMainFrame::CloseWindow() the window is closed twice, generating an
error from X.

